{"tid":1169123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"A21城巴搭客要求飛站直去港珠澳　打司機巴士撞壆","createTime":"2019-05-24T07:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T08:19:44.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c05f893f5f5c1a67c2c4f35d156780d00e934825","tid":1169123,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2834193/org/a7f9c661d41767caedd37f4dd5622c8b.jpg/yi3xgpCULMV8Kf1OzPaOP9nY4tRCie-qJg2MBSYNjAU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2834193%2Forg%2Fa7f9c661d41767caedd37f4dd5622c8b.jpg%2Fyi3xgpCULMV8Kf1OzPaOP9nY4tRCie-qJg2MBSYNjAU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=1e40eef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今（24日）早上6時50分，港珠澳橋人工島順環路158號港珠澳大橋城巴巴士站，有乘客報案指一輛A21城巴撞向石壆，劇烈搖晃導致身體不適。涉事巴士司機向警員報稱，行車期間曾被乘客襲擊。警方經初步調查，拘捕兩名涉事男子，分別為城巴巴士司機及乘客，涉嫌在公眾地方打鬥，案件交由大嶼山警區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進。據了解，兩人在巴士上起初因路線問題爭執，繼而動武，揮拳互毆，不久後巴士隨即撞壆。兩人報稱輕傷，送北大嶼山醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n乘客要求飛站直去人工島　拳打車長<br />\n<br />\n城巴發言人指，今日早上6時45分，一輛路線A21的巴士往機場方向行駛，途徑順輝路近港珠澳人工島時，一名乘客跟車長說車上已沒有其他乘客，認為巴士應直接駛往人工島，不用經過機場。兩人就此事起爭執，其間乘客揮拳打向司機，巴士失控撞向路壆。車長隨即通知公司及報警求助。城巴公司嚴厲遣責該名乘客行為，並會配合警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2834197/org/f53c26cce36379460ee3a40ba05d6f2e.jpg/CThUp_pJQZxIUoOYY28PuB_p5oiwuit6rr1BLoS9QS4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2834197%2Forg%2Ff53c26cce36379460ee3a40ba05d6f2e.jpg%2FCThUp_pJQZxIUoOYY28PuB_p5oiwuit6rr1BLoS9QS4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=6c18b24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路壆遺下碰撞痕跡。（賴雯心攝）<br />\n<br />\n所有A巴士　改道經港珠澳大橋口岸<br />\n<br />\n涉事A21巴士路線原本為機場巴士，來往紅磡站、尖沙咀、旺角及機場。因應港珠澳大橋於2018年10月24日通車，所有「A」開頭的機場巴士便在沒有諮詢情況下改動路線，包括涉事的A21路線，加設港珠澳大橋香港口岸站。當時曾惹來爭議，斥行車時間及承載量大增。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/332577/%E6%89%93%E5%88%B0%E6%92%9E%E8%BB%8A-a21%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%B4%E6%90%AD%E5%AE%A2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%A3%9B%E7%AB%99%E7%9B%B4%E5%8E%BB%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3-%E6%89%93%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E6%92%9E%E5%A3%86?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F332577%2F%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2592%259E%25E8%25BB%258A-a21%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%2590%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%25A3%259B%25E7%25AB%2599%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%258E%25BB%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%25A3%2586%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=22778a4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/332577/%E6%89%93%E5%88%B0%E6%92%9E%E8%BB%8A-a21%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%B4%E6%90%AD%E5%AE%A2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%A3%9B%E7%AB%99%E7%9B%B4%E5%8E%BB%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3-%E6%89%93%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E6%92%9E%E5%A3%86?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a>"},{"pid":"a1c44d10592cde88b4e5e8eaa2491eba797f14b1","tid":1169123,"uid":246419,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91ecea8a8cb1424e7905e5bf68d3c00a7b2d9e9","tid":1169123,"uid":41389,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"香港人係蝗蟲同基本法面前只能食屎 相信條友好快就會放出黎 警狗逼人簽和解書"},{"pid":"4f7eb5c63a38624f8ffcd837588ad057f70cbef2","tid":1169123,"uid":35430,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"生番就咪撚搭車啦仆街<br />\n趕住死，其他人要飛架仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用得港豬澳都係弱撚智"},{"pid":"c0cfe4ce583fd2ead89b7f39cb08959ee9d20a68","tid":1169123,"uid":173936,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"/城巴車長群組流傳更多有關今早A21車長受襲的經過：一名相信現職金巴車長、曾任職新巴的男子，於A21駛過機場1號客運大樓後，向A21車長表示自己是新巴車長，已經代為「巡車」，車上已無其他乘客，可以直接駛往港珠澳香港口岸，無需停2號客運大樓。但A21車長未有理會，結果被該男子襲擊，車長閃避時巴士失控撞向右邊石壆。<br />\n<br />\nA21 車長及乘客同時被警方以打架罪拘捕。城巴發言人表示強烈譴責有關襲擊行為。//"},{"pid":"e54b132e45933d5787cef8843e631b337ff6fc56","tid":1169123,"uid":35814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:14:00.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母支那蝗<br />\n唔比T2有客上車架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c90a007bb6f2df6e9c15027748811585b5e67c","tid":1169123,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"勿跟車太貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6565016bdc6d95e661aa941bcbf96acf4cfc7dfb","tid":1169123,"uid":48077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"上次大陸成架車跌落河 盲毛唔睇新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5bbc967cacb740daafbcf75b07a19e74391e82","tid":1169123,"uid":34348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因應港珠澳大橋於2018年10月24日通車，所有「A」開頭的機場巴士便在沒有諮詢情況下改動路線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nContent Farm 01又老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c6fd8d1d5eacffc46cdaabc315e0a9a2f94706","tid":1169123,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"路線問題起爭執　城巴車長與乘客互毆<br />\n<br />\n今早(24日)6時41分，一輛前往港珠澳大橋香港人工島的A21號線城巴，沿順暉路上橋往香港口岸旅檢大樓方向時，車內一名姓鄧(50歲)男乘客懷疑因路線問題，與姓鄭(54歲)車長發生爭吵，期間有人揮拳襲擊車長，雙方繼而大打出手，以拳互毆，未幾巴士失事撞向石壆，左車頭損毀，車上乘客於是報警求助。警方接報到場，經初步調查後，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架將2人拘捕，案件交由大嶼山警區刑事調查隊跟進。兩人均報稱身體痛，由救護車送院治療。 <br />\n<br />\n城巴發言人表示，事發時一名乘客向車長指巴士上沒有其他乘客，認為巴士應直接前往港珠澳大橋口岸，毋須駛經機場客運大樓，繼而與車長發生爭執，並打傷車長，巴士撞到石壆，車長即時通知公司及報警，並送院治理。公司嚴厲讉責襲擊車長行為，並會配合警方調查事件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190524/mobile/bkn-20190524073604455-0524_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190524%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190524073604455-0524_00822_001.html&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=7f4372a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190524/mobile/bkn-20190524073604455-0524_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"473471898ee1fb62e448d6a858e30d25913593a5","tid":1169123,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb5bbc967cacb740daafbcf75b07a19e74391e82","tid":1169123,"uid":34348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因應港珠澳大橋於2018年10月24日通車，所有「A」開頭的機場巴士便在沒有諮詢情況下改動路線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nContent Farm 01又老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:23:15.000Z","msg":"有上文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/252626/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4a%E5%B7%B4%E8%A6%81%E7%B6%93%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%BD%9F%E5%A4%9A%E6%AD%A4%E4%B8%80%E8%88%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F252626%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B-%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4a%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25B2%25B8-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BD%259F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2588%2589&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=61efe032\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/252626/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4a%E5%B7%B4%E8%A6%81%E7%B6%93%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%BD%9F%E5%A4%9A%E6%AD%A4%E4%B8%80%E8%88%89</a>"},{"pid":"c8cc9115da6d0a9aeb938d2e8c71192bd6f778b2","tid":1169123,"uid":37338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"大陸有個啊嬸打左巴士司機一巴判左四年，香港有無得學下？"},{"pid":"8e06d450098fbd113d9ee92e19640387fa799542","tid":1169123,"uid":34771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"唔好on9啦<br />\nA21要入T2接轉車客去港珠澳"},{"pid":"f18eab6cad5e8921e3e35e0e011d07ea2a655234","tid":1169123,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bb9d0b5f1fb8b485561067877ef8beed1d79f1b","tid":1169123,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"473471898ee1fb62e448d6a858e30d25913593a5","tid":1169123,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb5bbc967cacb740daafbcf75b07a19e74391e82","tid":1169123,"uid":34348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因應港珠澳大橋於2018年10月24日通車，所有「A」開頭的機場巴士便在沒有諮詢情況下改動路線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nContent Farm 01又老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:23:15.000Z","msg":"有上文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/252626/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4a%E5%B7%B4%E8%A6%81%E7%B6%93%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%BD%9F%E5%A4%9A%E6%AD%A4%E4%B8%80%E8%88%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F252626%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B-%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4a%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2